    "description": "Join the Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services family as a Distribution Manager in Varanasi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services:\nSnapdeal Logistics Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Snapdeal Logistics Holdings Services!",
